lead_paragraph: Taxi driver Ramazan Aktay is quick to shrug off the corruption scandal swirling around Turkish Prime Minister Tayyip Erdogan, at least as long as the ruling party keeps delivering free food and coal to his working class suburb of Ankara.

headline.main: Food and Fuel Trump Graft for Turkey's Local Elections
headline.print_headline: Food and Fuel Trump Graft for Turkey's Local Elections
